	<div style="text-align:right;">
		D´AMICO, Raissa Campos<sup>1</sup>; SLONGO, Helena<sup>2</sup>; BAENA, Cristina Pellegrino<sup>3</sup>		<BR>
		PIBIC		- Bolsa PUCPR-PIBIC		<BR>
